{"title":"HDU2197-本源串","uid":"db16d1c3f4775338fc6ee6b9aaac01fc","slug":"HDU2197","date":"2021-08-11T06:18:24.000Z","updated":"2021-08-15T07:40:39.521Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/HDU2197.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>简单的递归处理，或者说是思维题？</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h3 id=\"题意概括\"><a href=\"#题意概括\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题意概括\"></a>题意概括</h3><p>由0和1组成的串中，不能表示为由几个相同的较小的串连接成的串，称为本原串，有多少个长为n（n&lt;=100000000)的本原串？<br>答案mod2008。<br>例如，<strong>100100</strong>不是本原串，因为他是由两个<strong>100</strong>组成，而<strong>1101</strong>是本原串。</p>\n<h3 id=\"题目分析\"><a href=\"#题目分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目分析\"></a>题目分析</h3><p>简单递归。同样先分析简单情况——当其长度为1时，仅有1和2两种情况；当其长度为2时，则有10、01两种情况。向广泛情况推断，当我们目前有长度为n的一个本原串时，假设n有约数x，该串总能被划分为x份，且其不全部相同。而其划分的每一份又可以划分为更小的数，依次递归，最后可以回到长度为1、2的情况。最后，我们减去整个数列全是1、全是0的两种情况即可。</p>\n<h3 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">#include &lt;bits&#x2F;stdc++.h&gt;\n#define int long long\n#define mod 2008\nusing namespace std;\n\nint ksm(int a, int b) &#123;\n\tint res &#x3D; 1;\n\twhile (b) &#123;\n\t\tif (b &amp; 1) &#123;\n\t\t\tres *&#x3D; a;\n\t\t\tres %&#x3D; mod;\n\t\t&#125;\n\t\tb &gt;&gt;&#x3D; 1;\n\t\ta *&#x3D; a;\n\t\ta %&#x3D; mod;\n\t&#125;\n\treturn res;\n&#125;\n\nint dfs(int now) &#123;\n\tif (now &#x3D;&#x3D; 1)\n\t\treturn 2;\n\tint sum &#x3D; 0;\n\tfor (int i &#x3D; 2; i * i &lt;&#x3D; now; i++) &#123;\n\t\tif (now % i &#x3D;&#x3D; 0) &#123;\n\t\t\tsum &#x3D; (sum + dfs(i)) % mod;\n\t\t\tif (now &#x2F; i !&#x3D; i) &#123;\n\t\t\t\tsum &#x3D; (sum + dfs(now &#x2F; i)) % mod;\n\t\t\t&#125;\n\t\t&#125;\n\t&#125;\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;cout &lt;&lt; now &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; sum &lt;&lt; endl;\n\treturn (ksm(2, now) - sum - 2 + mod) % mod;\n&#125;\n\nsigned main() &#123;\n\tint n;\n\twhile (cin &gt;&gt; n) &#123;\n\t\t&#x2F;&#x2F;cout &lt;&lt; &quot;n:&quot; &lt;&lt; n &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t\tcout &lt;&lt; dfs(n) % mod &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t&#125;\n\treturn 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n","text":"简单的递归处理，或者说是思维题？ 题意概括由0和1组成的串中，不能表示为由几个相同的较小的串连接成的串，称为本原串，有多少个长为n（n&lt;=100000000)的本原串？答案mod2008。例如，100100不是本原串，因为他是由两个100组成，而1101是本原串。 题目分析...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"题解","slug":"题解","count":32,"path":"api/categories/题解.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"恢复OI实力","slug":"恢复OI实力","count":23,"path":"api/tags/恢复OI实力.json"},{"name":"递归","slug":"递归","count":1,"path":"api/tags/递归.json"},{"name":"HDU","slug":"HDU","count":3,"path":"api/tags/HDU.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E6%84%8F%E6%A6%82%E6%8B%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题意概括</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目分析</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/Bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/91730547"},"zhihu":{"icon":"/svg/Zhihu.svg","link":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/ying-zong-pai-wu-seng"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"CF616A-Comparing Two Long Integers","uid":"8e61ee85bd75ea7b8d3882c2cca36442","slug":"CF616A","date":"2021-08-12T03:35:23.000Z","updated":"2021-08-12T03:54:43.446Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CF616A.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"有关数位的简单模拟题。 题意概括给定两个数字序列a和b，根据其大小关系输出**&gt;、＜或=**；注意，两个序列的长度不超过$10^6$。 题目分析不怎么难的模拟题，抹除两个序列最前面0后，先比较数字序列的长度，若相等再逐位比较数字大小即可。 代码#include &lt;bi...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount"